      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773193579314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Why dropout is sbh?\n\nFor simplicity, it is\nassumed it take 1 byte\nto store every weight,\nthat it is active or\nnot, technicall it will be\n1/8.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "8_3m6cuIwFRXm3A_eQ4yM",
      "originalText": "Why dropout is sbh?\n\nFor simplicity, it is assumed it take 1 byte to store every weight, that it is active or not, technicall it will be 1/8.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
